- [ ] 1. Ma'lumotlar bazasi modellarini yangilash (`models.py`)
- [ ] 2. Shifokor holatlarini (FSM) yangilash (`doctor_actions.py`)
- [ ] 3. Xizmat qo'shish jarayoniga "Xarajat/Tannarx" qismini qo'shish (`doctor_profile.py`)
- [ ] 4. Shifokor profiliga "Moliyam" tugmasini kiritish
- [ ] 5. Moliya va Hisobot handlerlarini yozish (`doctor_finance.py`)
